    <item>
      <title>缅因州 ICE 枪击事件给参议员苏珊·柯林斯带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/ice-shooting-maine-susan-collins.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希望挑战弱势共和党人柯林斯女士的民主党人抓住了这一致命事件的机会，引起人们对她在移民问题上的记录的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/ice-shooting-maine-susan-collins.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 03:12:35 GMT</pubDate>
