    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示他周四的演讲将重点关注选举安全和投票机</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/trump-speech-voting-elections.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，计划在黄金时段发表讲话之际，政府工作组一直在努力解密文件，其中包括一些与选举有关的文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/trump-speech-voting-elections.html</guid>
