    <item>
      <title>再次与伊朗开战，特朗普找到了一个他无法轻易控制的对手</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/iran-trump-war.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位总统习惯于强迫其他国家屈服于他的意志。但随着他斡旋的停火协议破裂，他正在努力制定一项战略来迫使伊朗做出让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/iran-trump-war.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:01:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>父亲称，在缅因州被 ICE 杀害的哥伦比亚移民拥有合法身份</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/joan-sebastian-guerrero-maine-ice-shooting.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一被联邦移民特工枪杀的琼·塞巴斯蒂安·格雷罗 (Joan Sebastian Guerrero) 的父亲表示，他的儿子一直在打两份工来养活妻子和女儿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/joan-sebastian-guerrero-maine-ice-shooting.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 22:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ICE 枪击事件引发人们对执法记录仪缺乏的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/ice-body-cameras.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前国土安全部长克里斯蒂·诺姆五个月前表示，特朗普政府将“迅速”在全国各地的移民代理处部署随身摄像头。大约一半的人仍然没有。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/14/us/politics/ice-body-cameras.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 21:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
